                            <h1 class="or-page-title">
                                
	

                                ORCA’s Affordable Housing Pipeline
                            </h1>
                            <div class="form-group or-show-if-side-navigation">
                                <button class="btn btn-default btn-block hidden-md hidden-lg hidden-xl" type="button" data-toggle="offcanvas" data-target="#OregonSideNavigation" data-canvas="body"><span class="fa fa-bars notranslate" aria-hidden="true"></span> <span>Site Navigation</span></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    

                    

                        <div class="row">

                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <!-- side navigation publishing data source -->
                            

                            <!-- side navigation menu -->
                            <nav id="OregonSideNavigation" aria-label="Site Navigation" class="or-side-navigation navmenu navmenu-default navmenu-fixed-left offcanvas-sm">
	<ul class="nav">
		<li class=""><a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/Pages/default.aspx">Housing Development</a></li><li class="or-side-navigation-parent"><a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Pages/default.aspx">Oregon Centralized Application (ORCA)</a><div>
			<ul class="or-side-navigation-submenu list-unstyled">
				<li class=""><a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Pages/orca-how-to-apply.aspx">How to apply</a></li><li class=""><a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Pages/get-help-orca.aspx">Get Help with ORCA</a></li><li class="or-side-navigation-current"><a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Pages/current-pipeline.aspx" aria-current="page">ORCA’s Affordable Housing Pipeline</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div></li><li class=""><a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Pages/orca-outcomes.aspx">ORCA Outcomes and Key Impacts</a></li>
	</ul>
</nav>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-9" >

                    

                    
	

                    <!--Sharepoint's placeholder-->

                    
	
	
	
	
	
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ><p> Stay up to date on the status of ORCA projects in the pipeline&#58;<br></p><div><ul><li> <a href="https&#58;//data.oregon.gov/dataset/Pre-Application-Projects/fpms-5p9m/data_preview">Early-stage projects list</a>&#58; This list includes projects that have submitted an intake but haven’t yet completed a full application for funding.<br></li><li> <a href="https&#58;//data.oregon.gov/dataset/ORCA-applications-received/yqty-7sdj/data_preview">Active projects list</a>&#58; This list includes projects that have applied for funding and are working through the ORCA process, from impact assessment through commitment.</li><li><p>
            <a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Documents/orca-pipeline/orca-currently-available-resources-and-waitlist-2026-february.pdf">Projects on the waitlist&#58;</a> When there's more demand for funding than available money, projects are placed on a waitlist in the order in which applications were completed. These projects have completed the impact assessment step, and when new funding becomes available, they will be notified in order of their place on the waitlist. OHCS may ask applicants to update their application on the waitlist. Learn more about the waitlist policy in the 
            <a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Documents/how-to-apply/orca-manual-january-2026.pdf">ORCA Manual</a>.<br></p></li></ul></div><div><h2>Available Resources and ORCA Waitlist<br></h2><p>Stay up to date on the currently available development resources by referring to 
      <a href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Documents/orca-pipeline/orca-currently-available-resources-and-waitlist-2026-february.pdf">projects on the waitlist</a>.This information is updated monthly after each HSC meeting. OHCS staff can help developers determine the best fit for funding resources given eligibility requirements and resource availability.<br></p></div><div><h2>Funding Set-asides<br></h2><div>OHCS has “set-aside&quot; funding for specific organizations and geographic regions to relieve the housing burden of historically underserved populations and ensure investment in communities across Oregon.<br></div><p>
      <a class="ohcs-btn ohcs-btn-primary " href="/ohcs/rental-housing/housing-development/oregon-centralized-application-orca/Pages/orca-set-asides.aspx" target="_blank"> Learn more about ORCA Set-Asides </a> 
      <br> </p></div></div>
		</div>
	</div>

